1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 6=

3
00:00:12,520 --> 00:00:14,690
Nothing gets under a man's skin
like being told he can't.

4
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,839
(Just watch me. Today's the last day.)

5
00:00:17,079 --> 00:00:18,800
(I have to get Qiao Nian's body back.)

6
00:00:19,199 --> 00:00:19,800
Watch out!

7
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,520
I'm sorry!

8
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,240
I didn't mean to!

9
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:56,640
Hello?

10
00:00:57,159 --> 00:01:00,759
There's been an accident on Route 3,
Section 129, by the outskirts highway.

11
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:01,679
We need help.

12
00:01:01,679 --> 00:01:02,799
Hurry! Please hurry!

13
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:05,380
(Consciousness Space)

14
00:01:12,319 --> 00:01:16,359
Zechen!

15
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,640
Don't fall asleep, Zechen. Wake up!

16
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:24,439
Qiao Nian,

17
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:27,400
today's the seventh day.

18
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:30,599
You have to return to your own body.

19
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,840
I'm fine, Zechen.

20
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,159
Don't worry about me.

21
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,519
I'm getting you out first.

22
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,439
Whatever happens, don't fall asleep.

23
00:01:37,439 --> 00:01:38,239
Don't fall asleep.

24
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,159
Zechen, don't fall asleep.

25
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:41,840
Zechen...

26
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,480
Zechen...

27
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,640
Zechen...

28
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,959
He was struck by lightning?

29
00:01:58,799 --> 00:02:00,439
I'm back?

30
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,920
I'm really back!

31
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,400
Jiang Zechen.

32
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:06,599
Jiang Zechen!

33
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,439
Hurry!

34
00:02:12,250 --> 00:02:13,199
Qiao Nian, you're awake!

35
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:14,520
- Jiang Zechen!
- Careful!

36
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:18,599
Zechen!

37
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:20,360
Wake up, Jiang Zechen!

38
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,879
Zechen!

39
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:28,960
Zechen!

40
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,479
Zechen!

41
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,520
Zechen!

42
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,039
Are you okay?

43
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:50,680
Qiao Nian,

44
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:52,479
you're back.

45
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:54,479
Thank God.

46
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,879
Why isn't the ambulance here yet?

47
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,680
(Seriously? Struck by lightning again?)

48
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,439
Qiao Nian.

49
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:38,080
You're finally awake.

50
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,719
Song Che?

51
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,240
You've been out for a full day.

52
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:49,120
The hospital?

53
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,360
Why am I here?

54
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,479
And why are you here?

55
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:55,680
Qiao Nian!

56
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:01,000
Where is Qiao Nian?

57
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,960
Who?

58
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:05,759
A woman named Qiao Nian
was brought in with me.

59
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,000
Where is she now?

60
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,120
Oh, her?

61
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,199
She's in a VIP room.

62
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:13,639
So you're saying

63
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:15,960
that after I fell,

64
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:18,120
Qiao Wenjun took over the company,

65
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,639
and Grandpa couldn't stop her?

66
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:22,120
I was overseas

67
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,399
when I heard Jiang Zechen
had set you up.

68
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,160
I came back right away.

69
00:04:28,330 --> 00:04:30,199
Jiang Zechen,
what the hell are you doing here?

70
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,079
Don't touch Qiao Nian!

71
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,399
Qiao Nian,

72
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:37,720
you're okay.

73
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:39,800
Thank God you're okay.

74
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,439
(There he goes again.)

75
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,519
(I won't let him beat me to it.)

76
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:50,560
(I'm not falling for that again.)

77
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,920
Qiao Nian, I'm so glad you're back.

78
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,920
Jiang Zechen, let her go.

79
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,360
What about you? You okay?

80
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:02,040
I'm fine.

81
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:03,759
Jiang Zechen,

82
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:07,199
thanks for protecting me when I fell.

83
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,399
Fell?

84
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:11,439
Even so,

85
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,199
there's no going back for us now.

86
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,720
(I can't let them keep talking.)

87
00:05:17,110 --> 00:05:18,970
(I need to find a way
to get Qiao Nian back.)

88
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:21,800
Grandpa was my final straw.

89
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:25,920
I won't let anyone hurt him.

90
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,560
Wait.

91
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,839
(Is this because
of the lightning earlier?)

92
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:35,680
Don't tell me
you've forgotten everything

93
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,959
that happened after we fell.

94
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,040
Of course, I remember.

95
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:41,680
At the meeting, didn't you team
up with Qiao Wenjun

96
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,079
to go after my grandpa?

97
00:05:43,199 --> 00:05:44,519
Isn't that what happened?

98
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,560
Jiang Zechen, Qiao Nian just woke up.

99
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,399
Can you leave for now?

100
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:56,519
Qiao Nian, get some rest first.

101
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:59,480
Jiang Zechen, get out. Now.

102
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,680
I need to talk to you.

103
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:11,959
Wait for me. I'll be back.

104
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:22,879
Do you know if he married you
out of love?

105
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,519
Trash stays trash.

106
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:26,240
You'll never belong here.

107
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,040
(I'm done letting others control me.)

108
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:32,319
(I'm taking back everything
that's mine.)

109
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,319
You took Qiao Nian out of the hospital

110
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,319
and lured me into that car chase

111
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,439
just to get back at me?

112
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:48,079
And you? Why did you betray Qiao Nian?

113
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,100
If it weren't for you,

114
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:52,160
Qiao Nian wouldn't have suffered
like this.

115
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,639
She's my wife.

116
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:57,439
Why would I ever betray her or hurt her?

117
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,399
Is that so?

118
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:03,600
I heard you turned on her
at the shareholders' meeting.

119
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,279
I never should've let her go to you.

120
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,720
Not so you could hurt her like this!

121
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:11,360
If you're really
doing this for Qiao Nian,

122
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:17,519
then why are you working
with Qiao Wenjun?

123
00:07:17,759 --> 00:07:20,920
If I wasn't,
how else could I keep you in check?

124
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,240
Using business
to keep Qiao Wenjun in check?

125
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,390
You've really thought this through.

126
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:29,079
After all these years,

127
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:31,040
you still haven't moved on
from Qiao Nian.

128
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:35,839
If you think you can beat me,
you're far from it.

129
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,959
What is she to you, a trophy?

130
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:43,079
You don't deserve her.

131
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,720
From here on out,

132
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,680
stay out of this.

133
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:49,959
This has nothing to do with you.

134
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,360
(Jiang Zechen,)

135
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,160
(I'm going to beat you!)

136
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:57,460
(Westside Warehouse,
abandoned building)

137
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,560
You're finally here, Yiran.

138
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:10,399
What's this?

139
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:11,800
Nian,

140
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,079
where have you been all this time?

141
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,120
We were so worried about you.

142
00:08:16,399 --> 00:08:18,399
We thought you'd been kidnapped.

143
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,439
Kidnapped?

144
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:22,360
So you didn't know?

145
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:26,480
Looks like the kidnappers
were just messing with you.

146
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,720
They even demanded

147
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:32,159
the company's shares
in exchange for you.

148
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:35,960
And Grandpa is dead too.

149
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,759
Shut up!

150
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:40,720
Even if

151
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,759
you're just a stray Grandpa took in,

152
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:51,279
Mom and I remain the only family
you have now.

153
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,759
We won't abandon you.

154
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,879
Come home with us.

155
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,240
(Duan Yiran,)

156
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,000
(you finally took the bait.)

157
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:07,519
(Qiao Wenjun killed Grandpa.)

158
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,720
(There's no way
they'll let Nian go either.)

159
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:17,840
(What's going on?)

160
00:09:20,879 --> 00:09:21,679
(It's so hot.)

161
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:36,170
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

162
00:09:36,450 --> 00:09:44,050
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

163
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:47,890
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

164
00:09:48,410 --> 00:09:51,690
♪Where this ends♪

165
00:09:51,690 --> 00:09:58,970
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

166
00:09:58,970 --> 00:10:03,300
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

167
00:10:03,340 --> 00:10:06,420
♪Love turns into pain♪

168
00:10:06,490 --> 00:10:10,610
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

169
00:10:10,770 --> 00:10:14,250
♪Yet I still want you close♪

170
00:10:14,250 --> 00:10:18,420
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

171
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:21,730
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

172
00:10:21,730 --> 00:10:26,300
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

173
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:32,610
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

174
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:37,390
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

175
